::EndBringer/Scyther::

"Easy for you to say," Scyhter mutters to himself as he recieves 
DrillBit's transmission. He flies off toward the Council base, trying 
to throw Inferno off him.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
EndBringer recieves DrillBit's orders and takes off toward the edge 
of the mountain, wondering how he was going to climb down without 
being slagged.
